description:
This is a 22 minute workout called '20 MIN Beginner WALK & LIGHT JOG Treadmill Workout' from the channel IBX Running.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/Walking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Let's warm up those treadmills and join Coach Rachael for a Beginner Walk and Light Jog Workout. This is the perfect workout for those walkers or runners who don't want to jump into a full running workout quite yet. We will take it slow, but still sweaty, in this tread routine!

22:00 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!

Join our community of runners: http://www.ibxrunning.com
Merch: https://www.ibxrunning.com/store
IBX Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ibxrunning/
Veronica's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bodibyroni/
Rachael's Instragram: https://www.instagram.com/bedopefitness/

00:00 - Intro
00:43 - Warm Up
03:43 - Workout!
20:12 - Cool Down

Workout Structure:
Warmup: 3 minutes 
Part 1 - 5 Segments
      HILL WALK: 90 Seconds - 3.1 - 4.2 mph - 3.0 Incline
      Increase speed by 0.1 each segment
Part 2 - Repeat 4 times
      Jog: 90 Seconds - 4.0 - 6.0 mph
      Recover: 30 seconds -...
